sys_ui_page.html:
<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" ?>
<j:jelly trim="false" xmlns:j="jelly:core" xmlns:g="glide" xmlns:j2="null" xmlns:g2="null">
<g:evaluate jelly="true">
	var gr1 = new GlideRecord('x_tekso_twxapp01_setup');
	var url = '';
	gr1.query();
	if (gr1.next()) {
		var sys_id = gr1.getValue('sys_id');
		url = 'x_tekso_twxapp01_setup.do?sysparm_query=sys_id=' + sys_id.toString() + '&sysparm_stack=x_tekso_twxapp01_setup_list.do';
	}
	else{
		url = 'x_tekso_twxapp01_setup.do?sys_id=-1&sysparm_stack=x_tekso_twxapp01_setup_list.do';
	}
</g:evaluate>
<meta http-equiv="refresh" content="0;url=${url}" />
</j:jelly>
sys_ui_page.name: ui_page_to_redirect_to_setup
